  "title": "Hair Therapist / Hair Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Earn up to $3,000 monthly (Salary + Commission + Additional Incentive)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>6 Off Days per month</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Location near MRT, Bedok Area</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Employment: Full Time / Permanent</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Providing hair/scalp treatment services to clients</li>\n  <li>Update Sales Consultant of customers' scalp and hair condition and follow up</li>\n  <li>Emphasizes product benefits and upsell products/ services for customers' needs</li>\n  <li>Communicate with customers while delivering treatments</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 1 year experience in relevant hair industry</li>\n  <li>Able to work on retail hours including weekends and public holidays</li>\n  <li>Able to start on short notice/ immediate</li>\n  <li>Preferably bilingual (English/ Mandarin)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>职位：美发助理 /小埃 / 美发助理（头发和头皮）</strong></p>\n<p><strong>可赚取高达 $3,000月薪（底薪+佣金+额外奖励）</strong></p>\n<p><strong>每月休6天</strong></p>\n<p><strong>靠近地铁、勿洛地区</strong></p>\n<p><strong>就业：全职</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>职责</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>为客户提供头发/头皮治疗服务</li>\n  <li>通知顾问对于客户头皮和头发状况的了解并跟进</li>\n  <li>强调产品的优点，并根据客户的需求销售适合的产品与服务</li>\n  <li>提供治疗时与客户沟通</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>要求</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>至少1年相关美发/ 头皮护理行业的工作经验</li>\n  <li>能够在零售时间工作，包括周末和公共假期</li>\n  <li>能够在短时间内/ 立即开工</li>\n  <li>精通双语（英语 / 华语）</li>\n</ul>",
